Version History
---------------

Version 1.7 - Now mark/restores XMM handles and memory too.  Supports
              HIMEM.SYS, QEMM XMM manager, etc.  Full support for MS-DOS 5
              added, displays programs loaded with DOS 5's LOADHIGH.
              Works with Windows 3.0 in real, standard and enhanced modes.
              Works with programs using DPMI or VCPI memory interfaces.
              Fixed bug with reporting on serial ports and in particular
              with 16550AN UART chip.  Fixed some small bugs/errors in
              memory displays.

Version 1.6 - First shareware release.  Includes support for QEMM, 386-to-Max,
              QRAM, DESQview, all known EMS managers, etc.
